const SmileySad = (props) => {

    <svg
      className={props.className}
      id="smile-sad"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="42"
      height="42"
      viewBox="0 0 20 20"
    >
      <path
        id="Path_1219"
        data-name="Path 1219"
        d="M9,11a1,1,0,1,0-1-1A1,1,0,0,0,9,11Z"
        transform="translate(-2 -2)"
      />
      <path
        id="Path_1220"
        data-name="Path 1220"
        d="M14,17a2,2,0,0,0-4,0H8a4,4,0,0,1,8,0Z"

      />
      <path
        id="Path_1221"
        data-name="Path 1221"
        d="M16,10a1,1,0,1,1-1-1A1,1,0,0,1,16,10Z"
        transform="translate(-2 -2)"
      />
      <path
        id="Path_1222"
        data-name="Path 1222"
        d="M22,12A10,10,0,1,1,12,2,10,10,0,0,1,22,12Zm-2,0a8,8,0,1,1-8-8A8,8,0,0,1,20,12Z"
        transform="translate(-2 -2)"
        fill-rule="evenodd"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};

export default SmileySad;
